high_descs: Turn left and go to the round kitchen table.
Pick up the tea kettle from the table.
Turn around and move to the sink on the other side of the room.
Wash the tea kettle in the sink.
Turn around and go back to the kitchen table. Stop in between two chairs and in front of the spoon.
Set the tea kettle down between the fork and the edge of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the clean tea kettle on the table.

high_descs: Go left, and then another left past the island. Turn right to go to the brown table.
Pick up the tea pot on the table.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Place the tea pot in the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water off. Pick up the tea pot.
Take the tea pot and turn around. Go to the left and right a bit to find the brown table.
Place the tea pot on the table.
Turn left towards the fridge, then turn left to turn right towards the circle table.
Pick up the kettle from the table.
Turn around and walk towards the sink.
Place the kettle in the sink and fill it up with water.
Turn around and walk towards the circle table.
Place the kettle on the table.
anns.task_desc: Fill up the kettle with water.
